        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Informing Consumers about Smart Devices Act</strong></p> <p>This bill requires manufacturers of internet-connected devices (e.g., smart appliances) that are equipped with a camera or microphone to disclose to consumers that a camera or microphone is part of the device.</p> <p>The bill does not apply to mobile phones, laptops, or other devices that a consumer would reasonably expect to include a camera or microphone.</p>]]></text>
